# Bundled data notices

## HPO README fixture

`extdata/hpo-readme.obo` is a small derived fixture containing selected term
identifiers, labels, aliases, definitions, and relationships from the Human
Phenotype Ontology (HPO), <https://hpo.jax.org/>. It is included solely to run
the README without a network download. HPO is available under the Creative
Commons Attribution 4.0 International license (CC BY 4.0); see
<https://hpo.jax.org/app/license>.
